#TITLE

Expense Tracker 
A simple web app to track your income and expenses, helping you stay on top of your finances.

#FEATURES 

Add, edit, and delete transactions.
Categorize spending (e.g., Food, Salary).
View total income, expenses, and balance.
Responsive design for all devices.
Optional charts for spending insights.

#GETTING STARTED

Prerequisites
Node.js (v16+)
npm or yarn
Git

#INSTALLATION 
1. CLONE THE APP 

git clone https://github.com/your-username/expense-tracker.git
cd expense-tracker

2. INITIAL DEPENDANCIES 

npm install

3. START THE APP 

npm run dev

PROJECT STRUCTURE 

expense-tracker/
├── public/         # Static assets
├── src/            # Source code
│   ├── components/ # UI components
│   ├── pages/      # Page components
│   ├── App.tsx     # Main app
├── package.json    # Dependencies
├── README.md       # Docs

